      <h1 class='title'>Animal Welfare</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 cc30-1WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_31ws' title='Col. 31WS &mdash; HC Deb 27 October 2003 vol 412 c31WS' name='column_31ws' href='#column_31ws' rel='bookmark'>31WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04627'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_143'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gordon-marsden' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_143' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gordon Marsden' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gordon-marsden" title="Mr Gordon Marsden">Mr. Gordon Marsden</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04627">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs what steps her Department is taking to ensure that there will be no resumption of live exports of horses, ponies and donkeys for the meat trade from the United Kingdom. [134185]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0412P0-04628'>
        <a name='S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_144'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-ben-bradshaw' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0412P0_20031027_CWS2_144' title='Link to this speech by Mr Ben Bradshaw' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-ben-bradshaw" title="Mr Ben Bradshaw">Mr. Bradshaw</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0412P0-04628">We are taking the opportunity offered by negotiation of new EU rules on the welfare of animals in transport, to consider the best way to protect British equines.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
